Temperature normals for Waterville Maine (1991-2020)

Source: R/data.R
wat05.Rd

NOAA/NCEI derived normal daily temperatures for the city of Waterville, Maine (USA) for the 1991 to 2020 period. Units are in degrees Fahrenheit.

Usage

wat05

Format

A data frame with 365 rows and 5 variables:

date

Date centered on the 11991-2020 period. Note that the year is purely symbolic.

doy

Day of year.

min

Typical minimum temperature for the 1991-2020 period.

avg

Typical average temperature for the 1991-2020 period.

max

Typical maximum temperature for the 1991-2020 period.

...

Source

https://www.ncei.noaa.gov/
